'Good Heaven ! thought Martin . 
'The premises are on fire ! It was an alarm bell ! But there was no smoke to be seen , nor any flame , nor was there any smell of fire . 
Unable to bear it any longer , Martin followed . 
Even in his rapid progress he was run down , thrust aside , and passed , by two more gentlemen , stark mad , as it appeared , with fierce excitement . 
