Every sort of nateral advantage was connected with it , the agents said and there certainly was ONE , quite unlimited . 
No end to the water ! 'It's a thing he couldn't have done without , I suppose , observed Martin , peevishly . 
There it was , any way always turned on , and no water rate . 
Independent of three or four slimy old rivers close by , it varied on the farm from four to six foot deep in the dry season . 
He couldn't say how deep it was in the rainy time , for he never had anything long enough to sound it with . 
'Is this true ? asked Martin of his companion . 
