'He never was better than he is now . 
How are they all at home ? How's Charity ? 'Blooming , Mr Jonas , blooming . 
'And the other one how's she ? 'Volatile trifler ! said Mr Pecksniff , fondly musing . 
'She is well , she is well . 
'Well , well ! said Mr Pecksniff , with great feeling 'let me not be hard upon my child . 
Beside her sister Cherry she appears so . 
A strange noise that , Mr Jonas ! 'Something wrong in the clock , I suppose , said Jonas , glancing towards it . 
