Now it's come to this , I wouldn't be without a witness for a thousand pound . 
Chuffey said not a word , and heard not a word . 
He had sat himself down in a chair at the bedside , and there he remained , motionless except that he sometimes bent his head over the pillow , and seemed to listen . 
He never changed in this . 
'If anything happens Pecksniff , said Jonas , 'you must promise me to stop here till it's all over . 
