The other ladies were not at all behind hand in expressing similar sentiments and the children , of whom some scores had now collected , hooted and defied Mr Pecksniff quite savagely . 
So when Mrs Gamp appeared , the unoffending gentleman was glad to hustle her with very little ceremony into the cabriolet , and drive off , overwhelmed with popular execration . 
When she was disabused of this idea , her whole being resolved itself into an absorbing anxiety about her pattens , with which she played innumerable games at quoits on Mr Pecksniff's legs . 
