'An open handed gentleman ? cried Mrs Gamp , with enthusiasm . 
'No , no , said the undertaker 'not an open handed gentleman in general , by any means . 
Oh ! do not let us say that gold is dross , when it can buy such things as these , Mrs Gamp . 
'We should be an honoured calling . 
We do good by stealth , and blush to have it mentioned in our little bills . 
He had been a tender plant once upon a time , but from constant blowing in the fat atmosphere of funerals , had run to seed . 
