'You're very anxious I should stay , fright , ain't you ? 'Yes , I am , said Jonas . 
'Upon my word I am . 
I want to speak to you . 
But as she left the room notwithstanding , he ran out after her , and brought her back , after a short struggle in the passage which scandalized Miss Cherry very much . 
