A touch of fever and ague caught on these rivers , I dare say but bless you , THAT'S nothing . 
It's only a seasoning , and we must all be seasoned , one way or another . 
That's religion that is , you know , said Mark . 
He only sighed and shook his head . 
I won't be gone a minute . 
