'This may be a professional call . 
Indeed I am pretty sure it is . 
Seeing a gentleman and lady before him , he started back in as much confusion as a good man with a crystal conscience might betray in mere surprise . 
Pray , my dear sir , walk in . 
You find me in my garden dress . 
You will excuse it , I know . 
It is an ancient pursuit , gardening . 
Primitive , my dear sir . 
Or , if I am not mistaken , Adam was the first of our calling . 
He had by this time got them into the best parlour , where the portrait by Spiller , and the bust by Spoker , were . 
'My daughters , said Mr Pecksniff , 'will be overjoyed . 
