I hope in saying , Welcome to my humble roof ! I find some echo in her own sentiments . 
If features are an index to the heart , I have no fears of that . 
An extremely engaging expression of countenance , Mr Chuzzlewit , my dear sir very much so ! 'Mary , said the old man , 'Mr Pecksniff flatters you . 
But flattery from him is worth the having . 
He is not a dealer in it , and it comes from his heart . 
We thought Mr 'Pinch , said Mary . 
