What are legs ? Human nature . 
The conversation now becoming general , Mr Jonas's opinion was requested on this subject and as it was in full accordance with the sentiments of Mr Pip , that gentleman was extremely gratified . 
Indeed , both himself and Wolf had so much in common with Jonas , that they became very amicable and between their increasing friendship and the fumes of wine , Jonas grew talkative . 
