'It strikes one all of a heap . 
Wait a little bit ! I'm a coming round fast . 
That'll do ! These gentlemen ain't my friends . 
As they did not belong to the mansion , they were expelled by the two little boys . 
Not that I at all object to 'em . 
But one sees 'em to the best advantage out of doors perhaps . 
'How is it that you have come here ? asked the man , when their first expressions of surprise were over . 
