There's two or three American settlers left and they coolly comes over one , even here , sir , as if it was the wholesomest and loveliest spot in the world . 
But they're like the cock that went and hid himself to save his life , and was found out by the noise he made . 
They was born to do it , and do it they must , whatever comes of it . 
'Here's one on 'em , cried Mark , 'Hannibal Chollop . 
'Don't let him in , said Martin , feebly . 
