I HAVE gone ten foot , in a circ'lar di rection , but that was for a wager . 
'I hope you won it , sir , said Mark . 
'Well , sir , I realised the stakes , said Chollop . 
He was silent for a time , during which he was actively engaged in the formation of a magic circle round the chest on which he sat . 
When it was completed , he began to talk again . 
'How do you like our country , sir ? he inquired , looking at Martin . 
'Not at all , was the invalid's reply . 
Chollop continued to smoke without the least appearance of emotion , until he felt disposed to speak again . 
That time at length arriving , he took his pipe from his mouth , and said 'I am not surprised to hear you say so . 
It re quires An elevation , and A preparation of the intellect . 
The mind of man must be prepared for Freedom , Mr Co . 
'Why yes , sir , returned Mark . 
'I haven't a doubt about it myself . 
'Europian ! remarked Chollop , with sardonic pity . 
'Quite Europian ! And there he sat . 
Silent and cool , as if the house were his smoking away like a factory chimney . 
Mr Chollop was , of course , one of the most remarkable men in the country but he really was a notorious person besides . 
He also carried , amongst other trinkets , a sword stick , which he called his 'Tickler . 
he called 'Ripper , in allusion to its usefulness as a means of ventilating the stomach of any adversary in a close contest . 
Mr Chollop was a man of a roving disposition and , in any less advanced community , might have been mistaken for a violent vagabond . 
He had come to Eden on a speculation of this kind , but had abandoned it , and was about to leave . 
He called this 'planting the standard of civilization in the wilder gardens of My country . 
, but for the utter desolation and decay prevailing in the settlement , and his own approaching departure from it . 
As it was , he contented himself with showing Mark one of the revolving pistols , and asking him what he thought of that weapon . 
'It ain't long since I shot a man down with that , sir , in the State of IllinOY , observed Chollop . 
