You don't mean it to be answered , except in one way . 
Now , I don't choose to answer it in that way , for I cannot honestly answer it in that way . 
And therefore , I would rather not answer it at all . 
For if he could have got nothing out of him , he would have had to invent it for him , and that would have been laborious . 
He made a mental note of his answer , and went in again . 
