'You didn't ought to have received 'em , said the Captain . 
'We've come back alive , you see ! said Mark . 
'It ain't the thing I did expect , the Captain grumbled . 
'A man ain't got no right to be a public man , unless he meets the public views . 
Our fashionable people wouldn't have attended his le vee , if they had know'd it . 
Nothing mollified the Captain , who persisted in taking it very ill that they had not both died in Eden . 
