Each man took one slide forward as he was named butted at the Honourable Elijah Pogram with his head shook hands , and slid back again . 
The introductions being completed , the spokesman resumed . 
'Sir ! 'Mr Pogram ! cried the shrill boy . 
'Perhaps , said the spokesman , with a hopeless look , 'you will be so good , Dr . 
