I grieve to say that you were right in your estimate of his character . 
It may be a ridiculous weakness , John , but it has been very painful and bitter to me to find this out , I do assure you . 
Tom had no need to direct that appealing look towards his friend , in mild and gentle deprecation of his answering with a laugh . 
John Westlock would as soon have thought of striking him down upon the floor . 
'It was all a dream of mine , said Tom , 'and it is over . 
I'll tell you how it happened , at some other time . 
