He's afraid of me , I think . 
'It's my belief , said Tigg , 'that you are Poison to him . 
Nadgett ! give me that towel ! He had as little occasion for a towel as Jonas had for a start . 
But Nadgett brought it quickly and , having lingered for a moment , fell back upon his old post by the fire . 
