What the beef steak pudding would have come to , if it had not been by this time finished , astrology itself could hardly determine . 
'Tom , said Ruth , after a little hesitation , 'perhaps Mr Westlock , in his friendship for you , knows more of this than he chooses to tell . 
'No , indeed ! cried John , eagerly . 
