I'd scrape my shoes on the scraper of the door , and call that Pecksniff , if you liked but I wouldn't condescend no further . 
The amazement of Mrs Lupin , and indeed of Mr Tapley himself for that matter , at this impassioned flow of language , was immense . 
But Martin , after looking thoughtfully at the fire for a short time , said 'You are right , Mark . 
Right or wrong , it shall be done . 
