It was even a pleasanter breakfast than usual and it was always a pleasant one . 
I begin to think he will never come home again . 
What a mysterious life that man does lead , to be sure ! 'Very strange . 
Is it not , Tom ? 'Really , said Tom , 'I hope it is only strange . 
I hope there may be nothing wrong in it . 
