He succeeded , after great trouble , in engaging two garrets for himself and Mark , situated in a court in the Strand , not far from Temple Bar . 
It was swept and garnished for the reception of a visitor . 
For only keep the bedstead always in your mind and you were safe . 
That was the grand secret . 
Visitors were much assisted in their cautious efforts to preserve an unflagging recollection of this piece of furniture , by its size which was great . 
